channel.title: [317] Reokotsu - We have shit no one else does, come look
channel.description:
[center] [img]http://zxproductions.net/logo.png[/img] Reokotsu is a custom or non-custom 317 RuneScape Private Server depending on what you prefer. We give you the choice of logging into a version of Reokotsu with custom items, levels, abilities, or a non-custom version which only contains items from the real RuneScape. This may seem like two different server’s to some of you so let me explain. Both versions of Reokotsu save to one character file, so if you gain a level on one version then the other will also have the same level, same thing for items. Reokotsu is probably one of the most unique RSPS’ out there.
[b]Forums link:[/b] [url=http://zxproductions.net/Forums/activity.php]http://zxproductions.net/Forums/activity.php[/url]
[b]Webclient links:[/b] [url=http://www.zxproductions.net/ReoClient1.html]http://www.zxproductions.net/ReoClient1.html[/url] (custom server) [url=http://www.zxproductions.net/ReoClient2.html]http://www.zxproductions.net/ReoClient2.html[/url] (non-custom server)
[b]Features:[/b] Choice of either a custom server or non-custom server Clan chat Dicing (only when in a clan) No combat lag Npc clipping Very stable (once ran for over 250 hours straight without any kind of lag) Levels up to 133 (only on custom version) More balanced combat triangle 10x Hits, hit points, prayer Special abilities (only on custom version) Intense pking Donator shops Some rewritten skills for more smooth handling Run on VPS - don't see how this changes anything as long as we're 24/7 with no lag... which we are We're a leaned back community, as long as you don't break any of the rules we have no problem with you Frequent updates - we add stuff that we think of, not just stuff from tuts
[b]Bosses:[/b] General Graardor Giant mole Ice queen Dag kings Sea troll queen Zombie Champion Death wing Skeletal hellhound Corporal beast Chaos element TzTok-Jad (in fight caves)
[b]Mini-games:[/b] Castle wars Duel area Barrows Assault Fight pits Fight caves Pest control
[b]Custom Items:[/b] Full Torva Full Primal All Spirit shields Chaotic rapier Chaotic Maul Chaotic long sword Dragon pickaxe All PVP armours and weapons Korasi's sword Dragon claws Staff of light All Godswords Overloads 2nd - 4th gen Godswords (only on custom server) Full lava armour (only on custom server) Cursed Statius armour (only on custom server) Holy Vesta's armour (only on custom server) Ninja robes (only on custom server) Katana's (only on custom server) Chaotic daggers (only on custom server) Offhand whips (only on custom server) Cursed Saradomin sword (only on custom server) Light bow (only on custom server) Gilded bandos armour (only on custom server) Zetsumei war axes (only on custom server) Vampiric sword (only on custom server) Vampiric armour (only on custom server) Offhand items (we made before duel wielding on RS, only on custom server) Lots more custom items, I just listed the ones that came straight to my mind
[b]Pictures:[/b] [img]http://zxproductions.net/reo1.png[/img] [img]http://zxproductions.net/reo2.png[/img] [img]http://zxproductions.net/reo3.png[/img] [img]http://zxproductions.net/reo4.png[/img] [img]http://zxproductions.net/reo5.png[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/MdpzN.png[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/lcZnD.png[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/xn1Kt.png[/img]
If you want to see more pictures just tell me
[b]Note: If we're offline there's either been a Window's update or we're updating the server.[/b] [/center]
